# Mobile app for readers (e-readers)
- Greater accessibility and ownership of the book. The entire experience, from searching to reviewing, has been designed to ensure immersion.
- It's not required login to see the page, only to interact with other users and books.

## Pages
- Home: banner with ads and recommendation books (top stories), carousels by general, category, authors, etc. A search mode where an AI will search book.
- Bookcase: Show read stats and avaliable books to read.
- Read: Show the book the user is reading and when click open where it stopped.
- Social: place to connect with other readers and writers.
- Profile: The user profile to show your profile image, books, favorite authors and books.

## Immersion mode
- When enabled the user will not receive notifications and the reader page will open full screen.
- Everything is important to avoid distractions